    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346450/extras/82741338f1b43c898afd09055ec94a61.poster.avif?t=1766609627\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346450/extras/82741338f1b43c898afd09055ec94a61.webm?t=1766609627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346450/extras/82741338f1b43c898afd09055ec94a61.mp4?t=1766609627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2>In Rhythm Rabbit, you move automatically on the beat of the music, but the amount of steps (shown by the number of notes) changes on each move. You will have to quickly decide on which way to go, as the rabbit won't stop moving on the beat. The goal of each stage is to get to the carrot.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346450/extras/60c5ef36c480ee3ad74153f2aa4b7516.poster.avif?t=1766609627\" width=600 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346450/extras/60c5ef36c480ee3ad74153f2aa4b7516.webm?t=1766609627\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346450/extras/60c5ef36c480ee3ad74153f2aa4b7516.mp4?t=1766609627\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4 themed worlds to hop through<br></li><li>Wide range of enemies and environmental challenges<br></li><li>Incredibly challenging boss stages<br></li><li>Unlockable skins and soundtracks<br></li><li>Played with controller, mouse, keyboard or touchscreen<br></li><li>Also playable without sound</li></ul>",
